<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-ELIMINATE-RECAP-NYT </SLUG>
  
<TEXT>
<P>
   ALL BUDGETED STORIES HAVE MOVED.
</P>
<P>
   Recapping:
</P>
<P>
   The following were eliminated from tonight's NYTNS budgets:
</P>
<P>
   BRAZIL-ECON (Sao Paulo)
</P>
<P>
   HOUSING-REPORT (Washington)
</P>
<P>
   HKN-RHODEN-COLUMN (Undated)
</P>
<P>
   NATO-CREATION (Washington)
</P>
<P>
   KOSOVO-PENTAGON (Washington)
</P>
<P>
   KOSOVO-RUSSIA (Moscow)
</P>
<P>
   N.Y. Times News Service.
</P>
