wasn't sure but assumed not, and safely so. After all, he said,
it's ``not an urban school.'' It's away from all that urban danger,
just like the kids in rural Paducah, Ky., and Jonesboro, Ark., and
those at Springfield, Ore., or any place now labeled, ``Couldn't
Happen Here.'' (Young, Waco Tribune-Herald)
