<P>
   ROSENFELD-SHORTTAKES _ Themes have emerged from Littleton:
Outsiders. Revenge. Murder. Suicide. Hitler. Nazism. Medievalism.
Racism. Black coats. Ski masks. Bombs. Guns. A proud and prosperous
technocracy's burdens stirred into an occult brew, eye of toad,
tail of rat. (Rosenfeld, Cox News Service) MOVED WEDNESDAY.
