<P>
   MCNEELY-COLUMN _ AUSTIN, Texas _ There is a saying in lawmaking
circles about ``an idea whose time has come.'' But in Texas, school
vouchers may be an idea whose time never quite came, and now may be
receding. (McNeely, Austin American-Statesman) MOVED.
