<P>
   COXNET BOOKS 0422: LITERAY TITANS _ Ernest Hemingway and
Vladimir Nabokov could not have been more different. To mark the
100th anniversary of their births, there is a flurry of new and
re-issued books. Art includes one 3-column color illustration of
Hemingway and Nabokov.
</P>
<P>
   HEMINGWAY _ Ernest Hemingway once said he wanted no biography of
himself written while he was alive and preferably not for a hundred
years after he died. He was granted the first wish, but not the
second. (O'Briant, Atlanta Journal-Constitution) Art includes
1-column color illustration of Hemingway.
</P>
<P>
   HEMINGWAY LIST _ A list of forthcoming books about Hemingway.
