<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-04-22 14:45 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A9085 &Cx1f; tdt-z
u l &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-SHOOTING-ADVICE-BOS &LR;      04-22 0808
