<P>
   WATSON-STAR (Los Angeles) _ The first family of Hollywood, the
Watsons, will get a star on the Hollywood Walk of Fame. The
family's Hollywood history dates back to 1911 with patriarch Coy
Watson. It is estimated that the Watson family has appeared in more
than 1,000 films since that date. Seven honorees, six brothers and
one sister, are expected at the ceremony. By Doug Haberman. (Will
move in the ``n'' California and ``e'' entertainment news files.)
