<P>
   MEANS-COLUMN (Washington) _ Alas. The wine industry is under
siege. On one front lawmakers want to curb sales on the Internet.
On another, Sen. Strom Thurmond wants to raise excise taxes on wine
but not on hard liquor. By MARIANNE MEANS. (Already filed.)
</P>
