</HEADER>
<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-BOOKTAB-AUDIO25-COX </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
&HT;   
</HEADLINE>
 &HT;    List of new audio books
 &HT;    EDs: Embargoed for Sunday, April 25.
 &HT;    Staff reports
 &HT;    c. 1999 Cox News Service
<TEXT>
<P>
   Close Range: Wyoming Stories. By Annie Proulx. Simon &AMP; Schuster.
Four cassettes, five hours. $25. (May)
</P>
<P>
   England, England. By Julian Barnes. Dove Audio. Four cassettes,
six hours. $25. (May)
</P>
<P>
   The Girls' Guide to Hunting and Fishing. By Melissa Bank. Read
by the author. Penguin Audio. Two cassettes, three hours. $17.95.
(June)
</P>
<P>
   Local Girls. By Alice Hoffman. Reader TBA. Brilliance Audio. Two
cassettes, 3 hours. $17.95. Unabridged $39.95. (June)
