<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-04-22 21:41 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A9725 &Cx1f; tab-z
r a &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-HELPING-KIDS:MAXWELL-     04-22 1115
