ATTN EDITORS:  

</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
   The story BC-SHOOTING-BOS, by Mitchell Zuckoff (a), has moved.
</P>
<P>
   &QL; 
 &QL; 
 &UR; The Boston Globe &LR;  &QL;
</P>
